{"tid":1559701,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"入黎填野啦喂！","createTime":"2019-09-11T02:28:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-04T09:13:10.000Z","uid":171762,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cf5666de285c25247e3abca02e983c965899d87b","tid":1559701,"uid":171762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T02:28:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />9月16日截止喇! <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />快啲send email反對呀!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n教育局發佈諮詢文件嘅網頁: <a href=\"https://www.edb.gov.hk/tc/about-edb/press/consultation/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.edb.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fabout-edb%2Fpress%2Fconsultation%2F&d=3A5iQKMTOMHlOvaIjHeRelGN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=036532b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.edb.gov.hk/tc/about-edb/press/consultation/</a><br />\n是次諮詢文件直接連結: <a href=\"https://www.edb.gov.hk/attachment/tc/about-edb/press/consultation/TF_CurriculumReview_Consultation_c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.edb.gov.hk%2Fattachment%2Ftc%2Fabout-edb%2Fpress%2Fconsultation%2FTF_CurriculumReview_Consultation_c.pdf&d=3A5iQKMTOMHlOvaIjHeRelGN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=6abbbc2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.edb.gov.hk/attachment/tc/about-edb/press/consultation/TF_CurriculumReview_Consultation_c.pdf</a><br />\n新聞報導: <a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/社區專題/354111/中文課程改革1-dse中文刪聆聽-說話-前線老師批-行回頭路\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%A4%BE%E5%8D%80%E5%B0%88%E9%A1%8C%2F354111%2F%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%87%E8%AA%B2%E7%A8%8B%E6%94%B9%E9%9D%A91-dse%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%87%E5%88%AA%E8%81%86%E8%81%BD-%E8%AA%AA%E8%A9%B1-%E5%89%8D%E7%B7%9A%E8%80%81%E5%B8%AB%E6%89%B9-%E8%A1%8C%E5%9B%9E%E9%A0%AD%E8%B7%AF&d=3A5iQKMTOMHlOvaIjHeRelGN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=6fc636ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/社區專題/354111/中文課程改革1-dse中文刪聆聽-說話-前線老師批-行回頭路</a><br />\n<br />\n我知大家都懶得睇晒全份諮詢文件架喇，所以節錄咗以下部分大家最關心嘅內容:<br />\n<br />\n「中國語文和英國語文科有需要減少考試卷數及／或簡化校本評核以配合學生需要..... 至於中國語文科，可以探索公開考試的聆聽和／或說話部分，以及校本評核的實施是否可以修訂或減少以創造空間。」<br />\n「請於二零一九年九月十六日（星期一）或之前，以郵寄、電郵或傳真方式把書面意見交予專責小組秘書處：<br />\n郵寄地址： 香港灣仔<br />\n皇后大道東 213 號<br />\n胡忠大廈 13 樓 1301 室<br />\n學校課程檢討專責小組秘書處<br />\n電郵： taskforce_cur@edb.gov.hk<br />\n傳真號碼： (852) 2573 5299」<br />\n<br />\n以下係我嘅範例email (建議大家唔好照抄，有時間就改改佢啦)<br />\n<br />\n學校課程檢討專責小組諮詢文件 - 反對中國語文科刪減聆聽及說話卷<br />\n<br />\n敬啟者:<br />\n<br />\n本人閱畢學校課程檢討專責小組諮詢文件，現特意來函反對中學文憑試中國語文科刪減聆聽及說話卷的建議。<br />\n<br />\n報告認為中文為本港大部分學生的母語，故此質疑聆聽及說話卷的價值。以此論調，既然中文為大部分學生的母語，學生聽說讀寫的能力應該皆為上品，中國語文科根本不用考核，整科理應可刪去。事實上，聆聽及說話的能力當中更包含表達及理解能力，並不單單是母語與否的問題，從考評局的報告亦可見每年考生於聆聽及說話卷當中的表現參差，數據上已說明報告的說法並不合理。<br />\n<br />\n觀乎政府高官均以中文為母語，然則無法聆聽市民訴求，又於記者會上屢屢答非所問、內容貧乏、邏輯混亂，可見以中文為母語並不代表聆聽及說話能力必定理想。<br />\n<br />\n聆聽及說話均為重要能力，對學生升學及投身職場有絕大幫助。強於讀寫的學生不一定強於言語上的溝通，反之亦然。<br />\n<br />\n本人謹此強調，聽說讀寫，四大能力，缺一不可。<br />\n<br />\n此致<br />\n學校課程檢討專責小組秘書處<br />\n<br />\n市民<br />\n李老尾"},{"pid":"f0be9750d1f0c436d694fc259e31887117b9eddd","tid":1559701,"uid":52566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T02:28:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SZzaM4t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSZzaM4t.jpg&h=52a5a900&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dfb2ec1428aac89b0eebd0064df8942d049bd688","tid":1559701,"uid":171762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T02:29:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dce5f8d2ff1a1108e755b0f4199047a399917e87","tid":1559701,"uid":171762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T02:29:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"28115894d7b1979c198132b662a93a0b2472822d","tid":1559701,"uid":171762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T02:31:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1b8b162dcf10738c570cfce55e7a26a947f9203e","tid":1559701,"uid":171762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T02:52:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a987a09917acd2ab4924a96cc4e1fa5ac16ef438","tid":1559701,"uid":171762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T02:52:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"da9dbc785a8fbf88bdc8b9fbd5cb01c0f72d5831","tid":1559701,"uid":171762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T02:53:22.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"940162a342be9ca8d4664d56fc3ae9f823759b69","tid":1559701,"uid":170056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da9dbc785a8fbf88bdc8b9fbd5cb01c0f72d5831","tid":1559701,"uid":171762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T02:53:22.000Z","msg":"推呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T09:13:10.000Z","msg":"Sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}